	<p>Louisiana Center For Children's Rights does not now, nor will it in the future, sell, rent or lease any of our customer lists and/or names to any third parties.</p>

	<p>Louisiana Center for Children's Rights may disclose your personal information, without prior notice to you, only if required to do so in accordance with applicable laws and/or in a good faith belief that such action is deemed necessary or is required in an effort to:</p>

